      <hr style="width: 304px; background: #d7ad7b; height: 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">
      <p style="margin: 15px auto; color: #673011;">
        We are happy to inform you that Everything but the Chef is making improvements that  enhance our service! These changes are due to launch one week from today (on August 1st ) Perhaps most importantly, it will now be <strong>easy to get the Chef service absolutely FREE.</strong>
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 15px auto; color: #333;">
        The great news is that our meal plans will now be flexible. Members will be able to save "favorite" recipes from previous Chef meals and replace unwanted recipes with these favorites, as well as delete meal plans altogether if desired. In the near future we hope to offer members the ability to save their personal traditional family favorites and incorporate these into weekly meal plans also. 
      </p>
