      </p>
      <p style="margin: 15px auto; color: #333;">
        Look for these changes to occur next week and be sure to let us know what you think.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 15px auto 10px; color: #673011; font-weight: bold;">
        Yours in Cooking,
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 10px auto 30px; color: #673011; font-style: italic;">
        The Chef
      </p>
